1. Data: Over 13,000 BTC have flowed out of Coinbase Pro exchange wallets in the past 7 days;
2. CZ: Consider supporting some projects that adopt new token models;
3. CryptoQuant CEO: Ethereum has internal problems, and the team may no longer trust the leadership;
4. YZi Labs: Open project application portal to long-term builders
5. A giant whale withdrew 2,100 bitcoins from Binance in the past 24 hours, equivalent to about 180 million US dollars;
6. The total balance of bitcoins held by short-term BTC holders fell to the lowest level since October 2024;
7. A giant whale sold 531.7 billion PEPEs in the past hour, losing 7.02 million US dollars;
8. Vitalik's address transferred 90 ETH to an address 5 hours ago;
9. Japan's Finance Minister: It is possible to impose a 110% tax on crypto assets, but it is not limited to crypto assets;
10. Boyaa Interactive increased its holdings of 100 bitcoins, and the average purchase price was $79,500.
